feature_bullets: ✅ KRILL OIL BENEFITS - The omega-3 fatty acids in krill oil, primarily EPA and DHA, are believed to provide health benefits such as reducing inflammation throughout the body, improving heart health by reducing the risk of heart disease, and supporting cognitive function by improving memory, attention and mood.,✅ HEALTH BENEFITS - The phospholipids in krill oil, particularly phosphatidylcholine, are also thought to play a role in maintaining good health by supporting the structure and function of cell membranes, helping to transport fat-soluble vitamins and minerals, and promoting healthy brain function.,✅ MORE BENEFITS - Krill oil is also a good source of astaxanthin, a powerful antioxidant that can help protect the body against damage from free radicals and inflammation.,✅ BIOAVAILABILITY - Krill oil is more easily absorbed by the body compared to fish oil. You are guaranteed to receive a high-quality product that will help you achieve Better Health. You are also guaranteed to receive Freshly Produced supplements that are packed just after manufacturing.

name: Youth & Earth Superba™ Krill Oil 500mg (60 Softgels) Source of Omega 3s EPA, DHA and Astaxanthin
feature_bullets: 100% PURE KRILL OIL - Each capsule contains 500 mg of the purest krill oil from Aker Biomarine. The world leader in the harvest of Krill oil extracts its oil from clean North Antarctica. In these nutrient-filled waters, krill produces an oil rich in fatty acids and beneficial nutrients. They are committed to ensuring a reduced impact on the environment and the sustainable management of marine resources.,ENHANCED EFFICIENCY & SUPERBA BOOST - Superba Krill Oil increases both EPA and DHA omega-3 fatty acids more effectively than regular omega oil capsules. With important compounds like Marine Phospholipids, Phosphatidyl Choline, and Astaxanthin ensures that maximum benefit is obtained and differentiates krill oil from other fish oil supplements. By including Superba in your daily healthcare routine, you will be taking a more productive approach to optimizing your health as you age.,EPA AND DHA SUPPLEMENT- Our Krill Oil capsules contain astaxanthin (the natural red pigment). Astaxanthin with phospholipids offers valuable benefits to the body due to its ability to neutralize free radicals. It also has a high content of eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA). The krill oil boost can help delay the signs of skin aging, support the immune system boost, fight tiredness, and improve mood, mental and sports performance.,SOURCE OF OMEGA-3 FATTY ACIDS & CHOLINE SUPPLEMENT- The composition of the krill oil is based on flexible phospholipids. As a natural source of Omega-3, it's rich in eicosapentaenoic and docosahexaenoic acids and has better bioavailability than other natural sources of Omega-3. It also has a high content of natural antioxidants. Particularly notable is its content in astaxanthin, a very active antioxidant and the substance that gives the krill reddish color.,THE HIGHEST QUALITY KRILL OIL CAPSULES - At Youth & Earth, we know you only want the best for your body. We want that too and so we NEVER compromise when it comes to quality. We only put our name to products that are the very best on the market. Our packaging is recyclable & environmentally friendly, we use sustainable materials, such as glass & rice paper, and we source products that are plant-based & natural.

feature_bullets: OMEGA-3 ENHANCED: Superba Krill Oil, clinically proven to increase omega-3 fatty acid levels in the body, Omega-3 Fatty Acids, Omega-3 Phospholipids and Natural Astaxanthin. The specialty of Krill Omega-3 fatty acids is that they are bound to phospholipids, a class of lipids that are a main component of all cell membranes. Phospholipids support the distribution of omega-3 fatty acids in the body, which means that it is better absorbed by the body than all other omega fatty acid sources.,BEST FORMULA: Krill Oil (Superba Extract) 500mg and we recommend per 2 Softgels Providing: Per 2 capsule serving: Krill Oil Extract 1000mg. Marine Gel Capsules. This provides: Marine Phospholipids 430mg Total Omega 3 240mg Eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 140mg, Docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 65mg Astaxanthin 80ug.,PREMIUM QUALITY: Contains 500mg of Krill oil per softgel with more naturally occurring EPA, DHA, Phospholipids and Astaxanthin. Astaxanthin is a natural dye that is responsible for the red color of the krill and is considered an antioxidant. Various researches have shown that the dye astaxanthin has up to a hundred times more activity than an antioxidant than all previously known active ingredients.,100% NATURAL: Superba Krill has also been shown to increase the Omega-3 Index faster and more efficiently compared to other marine sources. Unlike other sources of Omega 3 such as fish oil, Superba Krill Oil requires no refining. This is because Superba Krill is harvested from the pristine clean waters of the Antarctic Ocean.,BUY WITH CONFIDENCE: Finest sourced and freshest Krill direct from the Antarctic.

feature_bullets: Super B Plus Group Ltd Antarctic Krill Oil Superba capsules is sustainably sourced from the cleanest water of the Antarctic Ocean. Created with nature in mind to give you enough nutrition for your daily health plans. Our Antarctic Krill Oil Superba delivers Omega-3 essential fatty acids EPA & DHA in their most natural form with high concentration of Phospholipids for superior absorption. Our high-strength formula provides 500mg of krill oil per softgel capsule for easy daily intake.,Our unique formulation contains two types of omega-3 fatty acid: eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) to provide support for heart, liver, immunity, energy, bones, brain, hair, skin, nails, vision and more! EPA & DHA contribute to the maintenance of normal blood triglyceride levels & blood pressure & normal function of the heart. DHA contributes to the maintenance of normal brain function & vision.,Antarctic krill oil there is no fishy odour or after-taste! Our red krill oil capsules 500mg are a good source of Omega 3 with marine phospholipids that are better utilised in the body than Omega 3 fish oil. name: Antarctic Krill Oil Omega Boosting Cod Liver Oil Alternative. A Potent Source of EPA, Astaxanthin & DHA for Brain Function, Heart Health, Blood, Hair, Skin, Joints, Connective Tissues & Liver
feature_bullets: When a proper balance of omega-6s to omega-3s is achieved, both your body and mind both reap a number of benefits. Krill oil is a supplement that is rapidly gaining popularity as an alternative to fish oil. It is made from krill, a type of small crustacean consumed by whales, penguins and other sea creatures. It may offer unique benefits such as a smaller dosage, antioxidants, sustainable sourcing and fewer side effects in comparison to regular Fish Oils.,Roughly 20 % of your brain is made up of the essential omega 3 fatty acid DHA which supports the performance of your brain serving as membrane component. You want to support your thinking, your mental energy and your spiritual vitality? Antarctic Krill Oil Omega Boost is your answer.,The fats found in krill oil may be easier for the body to use than those from fish oil, since most omega-3 fats in fish oil are stored in the form of triglycerides. On the other hand, a large portion of the omega-3 fats in krill oil can be found in the form of molecules called phospholipids, which may be easier to absorb into the bloodstream.,Krill oil is used for the same reasons as cod liver oil, flax oil and other omega 3 fatty acids, but is often favoured because it does not cause fishy burps or an after-taste - a common side effect of fish oil. In fact, krill oil may be even more effective at fighting inflammation than other marine omega-3 sources because it appears to be easier for the body to use.,What’s more, krill oil contains a pink-orange pigment called astaxanthin, which may help reduce infammation with antioxidant effects. In fact, a study that found krill oil significantly reduced a marker of inflammation also found that krill oil reduced stiffness, functional impairment and pain in patients with rheumat0id or oste0arthr!tis. It also increased their range of motion.
